summary: Creates new male character presets for Imperial and Breton race.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#ff0000][size=4][b]THIS MOD IS NO LONGER SUPPORTED BY THE AUTHOR[/b][/size][/color]


Creates new male character presets for Imperial and Breton races (more on the way). They will be the very last presets on the scale. Haven't really tested it, but should be unique, since they're not replacements of existing presets, but completely new ones.

Drop the file into Steam\SteamApps\common\skyrim\Data folder


[color=#ff6666] [b] [u] PLEASE, REMEMBER TO ENDORSE THE FILE IF YOU LIKE IT. IT ISN'T MUCH TO ASK, BUT IT MAKES IT WORTHWILE FOR ME. [/u] [/b] [/color]




[b] [color=#ff3366] THE CHARACTERS IN THE SCREENSHOTS USE TEXTURES FROM [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=1971] SMOOTH FACES FOR LADIES AND GENTS[/url] AND [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3424] PRETTY EYES [/url] MODS [/color] [/b]


[b][color=#cc9933]THE IMPERIAL PRESET GUY IS AVAILABLE AS A MAGE FOLLOWER IN THIS MOD: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21683]FELIX CONSTANTINE, FOLLOWER EXTRAORDINAIRE[/url].[/color][/b]

[color=#ff6666] Let me know if there are any bugs. [/color]
author: pikkatze
